{"tid":766596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳台人士支那就業毋須再辦許可證","createTime":"2018-08-03T16:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T02:29:11.000Z","uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a47c1dc0853a90552a795fd67f110e3e14eb2547","tid":766596,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"國務院今日公布取消11項行政許可，當中包括港澳台人士在內地就業要先取得當局許可的制度。<br />\n<br />\n內地2005年發布《關於建立勞動用工備案制度的通知》，要求用人單位需建立勞動用工備案制度，規定境外、包括港澳台人士在內地工作，實行就業許可制度，任何單位或個人聘用境外人士在內地工作，均要辦理就業證等相關手續。<br />\n<br />\n據國務院最新規定，相關審批取消後，人力資源社會保障部會通過以下措施加強事中事後監管，包括在港澳台人員就業服務、社會保障、失業登記、勞動權益保護等方面，盡快推出配套政策措施，並指導督促地方人力資源社會保障部門落實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180803/s00004/1533291586621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180803%2Fs00004%2F1533291586621&d=Y33Wh5SlbbBhD2ieEQzgBAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=7693782a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180803%2Fs00004%2F1533291586621&h=a4e2cd3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180803/s00004/1533291586621</a><br />\n<br />\n2025機會來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6a2d3fd189a75be056ec2a6af4e95b62826763","tid":766596,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34bc4f361c7967d78f8a04b664ff8dad09c3fdcc","tid":766596,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e439da041e988d81cc42d09a69dddfabc2ee97c","tid":766596,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:28:57.000Z","msg":"正式輸入港奴"},{"pid":"88b439638895d4bb6d